hadiths[14]{hadithnumber,text}:
530,"Eid key liye pedal jana aur nikalney sey pehley kuchh kha lena sunnat hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai wo mustahab samajhtey hain ke aadmi eid key liye pedal jaey aur Eid-Ul-Fitr ki namaz key liye nikalney sey pehley kuchh kha le. 3- mustahab ye hai ke aadmi bila uzr sawar ho kar na jaey."
531,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma eidain ki namaz khutbe sey pehley padhtey aur uskey baad khutba detey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke eidain ki namaz khutbe sey pehley hogi. 4- aur kaha jata hai ke sab sey pehley jisney namaz sey pehley khutba diya wo Marwan bin Hakam tha.
532,Mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Eidain ki namaz eik aur do sey ziyada baar yani mutaaddid (bahutsi) baar baghair Azan aur baghair iqaamat key padhi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir bin Abdullah aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai ke Eidain ki namaz key liye Azan nahin di jaeygi aur na nawaafil mein sey kisi key liye.
533,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eidain aur Jume mein (سبح اسم ربك الأعلى) aur (هل أتاك حديث الغاشية) padhtey they, aur kabhi-kabhi dono eik hi din mein aa padtey to bhi unhi dono Suraton ko padhtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu Waqid , Samura bin Jundub aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur isi tarah Sufiyan Sory aur Musa'ir ney bhi Ibrahim bin Muhammad bin Muntashir sey Abu Awaana ki hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai. 4- rahey Sufiyan bin Uena to un sey riwayat mein ikhtilaf paya jata hai. un ki eik sanad yun hai : (عن إبراهيم بن محمد بن المنتشر an أبيه an حبيب بن سالم an أبيه an النعمان بن بشير) ‏‏‏‏aur ham Habib bin Salim ki kisi aisi riwayat ko nahin jantey jisey unhoney apney walid sey riwayat ki ho. Habib bin Salim Noman bin Bashir key azad karda ghulam hain, unhoney Noman bin Bashir sey kaee ahadees riwayat ki hain. aur ibne Uena sey Ibrahim bin Muhammad bin Muntashir ke wastey sey un logon ki tarah bhi riwayat ki gaee hai padhi. aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap eidain ki namaz mein « sura Qaaf » aur «Sura Qamar » padhtey they padhi. aur yehi Shafai bhi kehtey hain."
534,umr bin Khattab ney Abu Waqid Laisi Haris bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : Eidul-Fitra aur Eidul-Azhaa mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kya padhtey they? unhoney kaha : aap Sura Qaaf aur Sura Qamar padhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
535,Isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai.
536,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Eidain mein pehli rakat mein qirat sey pehley saat aur dusri rakat mein qirat sey pehley paanch takbeerein kahin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Aaisha , ibne-Umar aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- Kasir ke dada ki hadees Hasan hai aur ye sab sey achchhi riwayat hai jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is baab mein riwayat ki gaee hai. padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, 4- aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney Madiney mein isi tarah ye namaz padhi , 5- aur yehi ehale Madina ka bhi qol hai, aur yehi Malik bin Anas , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain, 6- Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney Eidain ki takbeeron key barey mein kaha hai ke ye no takbeerein hain. pehli rakat mein qirat sey pehley paanch takbeerein kahey padhi. aur dusri rakat mein pehley qirat karey phir rukoo ki takbir key sath chaar takbeerein kahey padhi. kaee Sahaba kiram sey bhi isi tarah ki riwayat marvi (riwayat hui) hai. ehle-koofa ka bhi qol yehi hai aur yehi Sufiyan Sory bhi kehtey hain."
537,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Eidul-Fitr ke din nikley, aap ney do rakat namaz padhi, phir aap ney na is sey pehley koi namaz padhi aur na uskey baad. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin umr , Abdullah bin Amr aur abu-Saeed sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, aur yehi Shafai , Ahmed , aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain, 4- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm key eik giroh ka khayal hai ke Eidain ki namaz ke pehley aur uskey baad namaz padh saktey hain lekin pehla qol ziyada sahih hai."
538,wo eid key din nikley to unhoney na is sey pehley koi namaz padhi aur na uskey baad aur zikr kiya ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aisey hi kiya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
539,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Eidain mein kanwari ladkiyon,parda nasheen aur haaiza aurton ko bhi ley jatey they. albatta haaiza aurten Eid-gaah sey door rehti aur musalmanon ki dua mein shareek rehti. eik aurat ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! agar kisi aurat key paas chadar na ho to kya karey?  aap ney farmaya : ''uski behan ko chahiye ke usey apni chaadaron mein sey koi chadar udhaar  dedey.''"
540,"Umme Atiya (Raziallahu Anha) sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Umme Atiya (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm isi hadees ki taraf gaey hain aur Eidain key liye aurton ko nikalney ki rukhsat (choot) di hai, aur baaz ney isey makrooh jana hai. 4- Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain ke aaj kal mein Eidain mein aurton key janey ko makrooh samajhta hun, agar koi aurat na maaney aur nikalney hi par ba-zid ho to chahiye ke uska shohar usey puraney maile kapdon mein nikalney ki ijazat dey aur wo zeenat na karey. aur agar wo is tarah nikalney par razi na ho to phir shohar ko haq hai ke wo usey nikalney sey rok dey. 5- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey naqal kiya hai ke agar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam un naee chizon ko dekh letey jo ab aurton ney nikal rakhi hain to unhen masjid janey sey mana farma detey jaisey Bani-Israel ki aurton ko mana kar diya gaya tha. 6- Sufiyan Sory sey bhi naqal kiya gaya hai ke aaj kal key daur mein unhoney bhi aurton ka Eid key liye nikalna makrooh qarar diya."
541,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab Eid key din eik raastey sey nikaltey to doosrey sey wapis aatey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin umr aur abu-Raafey (Raziallauh anhum) sey hadeesen aai hain. 3- Abu-Tameela aur Yunus bin Muhammad ney ye hadees b-tareeq : « Fulaih bin Suleman, an Saeed bin al-Haaris, an Jabir bin Abdullah» ki hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ney is hadees ki perwi mein Imam key liye mustahab qarar diya hai ke jab eik raastey sey jaey to doosrey sey wapis aaye. Shafai ka yehi qol hai, aur Jabir ki hadees (ba-muqabla abu-Huraira) goya ziyada sahih hai."
542,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eidul-Fitr key din jab tak kha na letey nikaltey nahin they aur eidul-Azha key din jab tak namaz na padh letey khatey na they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Barida bin haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees gharib hai, 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke sawab bin Utba ki uskey ilawa koi hadees mujhey nahin malum , padhi. 3- is bab mein Ali aur Anas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- baaz ehle-ilm ney mustahab qarar diya hai ke aadmi eidul-Fitr ki namaz key liye kuch khaye baghair na nikley aur uskey liye mustahab ye hai ke wo khajoor padhi. ka nashta karey aur eidul-Azha key din na khaye jab tak ke lot kar na aa jaey ."
543,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eidul-Fitr key din namaz key liye nikalney sey pehley chand khajuren kha letey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai.
